      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SINALOA BANDIT (4) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 14 lengths away in fifth (31.23). Was in the money the start prior. Form from her last run is proving very strong. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. STATUE OF TIME (1) box seated before sticking on well to finish one length away in second (34.47) at this track in a Grade 5/6 over 595m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Bold showing expected. IZZY LETTS (2) ran a good time (22.44) when placing three back at Murray Bridge but has missed the frame since, last time out finishing fourth (35.14) at this track. Can feature with the right run. SMOOTH DYNAMITE (5) has been freshened for this and can hit the frame.",
